name: Power in Words 5
description:
Quote: Never underestimate anybody. It might be too late once you realize their worth. —Toni Payne 


Words can be very powerful. They can influence our day and change our lives. They can make us happy or sad, and even motivate us to be the best we can possibly be. Words can shape our very existence. The Power in Words is a collection of relatable Quotes by Toni Payne created to inspire and motivate.
